    "content": "3D Printed Parts 3mf File:\nUno_Ethernet_Enclosure-Box.3mf Digital I/O Components\rCreate Holes in Encloser\rMount Components\rWiring Schematic - Input (Button)\rWiring Schematic - Output (LEDs)\rWiring Schematic - Overview for this lab\rInfoThis wiring schematic shows a 24VDC. The Fortinet Power Supply is 48VDC only, thus a seperate Power Supply is REQUIRED. The 12VDC Power Supply listed in the Digital I/O BOM is the suggested Power Supply Final Assembly\rNoteIn the picture below a 24VDC power supply is “sandwiched” between the two Fortinet Power Supplies. The 12VDC Power Supply listed in the Digital I/O BOM is the suggested Power Supply",
