    "content": "If you get the error No route to host with any of the following steps, use the Troubleshoot Ansible steps ​\rRDP to OOB\rfrom Terminal in OOB cd /home/fortinet/automation/ansible/ubuntu ./create_ubuntu_vm.sh ../vars/all-hosts.yml \u003cPVE server name\u003e ubuntu_sdwan ./start_stop_remove_vm.sh ../vars/all-hosts.yml \u003cPVE server name\u003e ubuntu_sdwan started\r​\rContinuing from Terminal in OOB\rMake sure Ubuntu-x VMs have fully started (i.e. GUI is up and running) before exeucting the following. Suggest opening console windows on PVE to verify. ./wallpaper_update.sh ubuntu_sdwan",
